        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         Hitsmodes is a window that will filter out your hits, others hits and misses from the chat window. </P><P>/doability will press whatever ability button you have selected. For example.</P><P>Backstab is in slot one, you could do /doability 1 and it will press the backstab button. This is really only used for macros. For example a rogue might make a hotkey to evade the mob.</P><P>/attack off<BR>/doability 1<BR>/doability 2<BR>/attack on</P><P>This will, Turn attack off, press the pickpocket button, and press the hide button, then turn back on attack.</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
